    <p>I briefly explored using Valve‚Äôs Destinations software with photogrammetry, but the fact that it was December in Boston meant that finding a vineyard to tour and photograph would be a challenge (and likely unsuitable).</p>
    <p>As I write this (early 2017) much of my VR prototyping is now done in <a href="http://aframe.io" target="_blank">A-Frame.</a> For a run-down of the most popular VR-compatible SDKs and headsets, check out <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rJmdeLeBVI0yXaGykWytt6n8qKjnomBGhk3fagAiufg/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">this document.</a></p>
